    ("A","medium",2024,"The slope of a velocity-time graph gives:","Acceleration","Displacement","Speed","Distance","Slope of v-t graph = Δv/Δt = acceleration. Area under v-t graph = displacement.","वेग-समय ग्राफ की ढाल क्या देती है:","त्वरण","विस्थापन","चाल","दूरी","v-t ग्राफ की ढाल = Δv/Δt = त्वरण। v-t ग्राफ के नीचे क्षेत्रफल = विस्थापन।"),
    ("B","easy",2024,"The SI unit of speed is:","km/h","m/s","cm/s","m/s²","Speed (scalar) and velocity (vector) both have SI unit m/s (meter per second).","चाल की SI इकाई है:","km/h","m/s","cm/s","m/s²","चाल (अदिश) और वेग (सदिश) दोनों की SI इकाई m/s (मीटर प्रति सेकंड) है।"),
